title: New Avengers Trailer Reveals An Endgame
body:
New Avengers Trailer Reveals An Endgame

Marvel has finally released a trailer for the fourth Avengers film, which will be called Avengers: Endgame. The full title was cause for much speculation with subtitles ranging from “Infinity Gauntlet” to “Reassembled.” The trailer offers just a few glimpses of Tony Stark (Robert Downey Jr.) and Captain America (Chris Evans) after Thanos (Josh Brolin) snapped his fingers — an event now known as…

You guys had one job…

Apparently the Captain Marvel trailer came out THREE DAYS AGO and I just found out from an edit. AN EDIT. One of the main reasons I’m on here is to stay up to date.
